  <answer><![CDATA[<p>We really hope that you don’t have reason to cancel your holiday arrangements with us, but if you do, we ask that you let us, or your travel agent know immediately.</p>
<p>If you have booked directly with Inghams, please call Reservations on <strong>01486 791111</strong>. Please note that if you have booked via a travel agency, you must cancel with them directly.</p>]]></answer>
